{"tid":117424,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"睇好啟德變太古。慈父:「人生如賭博」","createTime":"2017-02-12T08:24:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-12T09:18:32.000Z","uid":29314,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4a9bb375c0ed28946e4c1f1393409fe20c4a4007","tid":117424,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T08:24:01.000Z","msg":"現居太古城的退休人士郭先生，有意入市啟德嘉匯兩房單位予仔女，預算800萬元，自己畀一半首期，仔女供，呢個樓價係極限啦。因為唔畀多啲首期，銀行未必咁易借錢，佢哋又供得辛苦。<br />\n<br />\n之前啟德1號開售，自己冇乜留意，但<span style=\"color: red;\">見到海航用1.3萬係咁搶地，就改變睇法，認為啟德有發展前景。</span>"},{"pid":"48479916b6811eec7bc4431e730391be571f4c97","tid":117424,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T08:24:39.000Z","msg":"他看好啟德未來發展媲美太古城。問他為何對啟德咁有信心，<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n他回應「人生如賭博」"},{"pid":"650d11a586dcbb270da38322bad72905820984a2","tid":117424,"uid":29898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T08:26:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>他看好啟德未來發展媲美太古城。問他為何對啟德咁有信心，<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n他回應「人生如賭博」</blockquote><br />\n其實講得岩"},{"pid":"f0686b2c00024a5f7e01d7653f4cefbed788a678","tid":117424,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T08:27:30.000Z","msg":"起碼老豆出4m去賭"},{"pid":"6f9946e2b9820d5df3554a36780a297ae77e76da","tid":117424,"uid":43308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T08:27:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b3707ef674c466ba5c85b44aa6ee7b813205a0c2","tid":117424,"uid":43308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T08:28:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4a93602b7e0dfbdb4c5ff61243fe80f9aee8d71a","tid":117424,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T08:29:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>真正慈父</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n肯畀錢就係「慈父」<br />\n<br />\n同一道理，肯畀錢就係「孝子」"},{"pid":"94b9097a9be5b1cee5fd370a4c7d9b0321d9ac17","tid":117424,"uid":31962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T08:33:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>他看